data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531331\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qmi1665702875884.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qmi1665702875884.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qmi1665702875884.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qmi1665702875884\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Unicode-Related Settings and ProcScript Instructions\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Assignment settings and ProcScript instructions influence the use of Unicode in your applications.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qmi1665702875884__section_w7743ab1b5b1_w7744ab1b5_w7745ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2930e1_d2931e1_d2932e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Unicode-Related Assignment Settings</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2930e1_d2931e1_d2932e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Setting</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2930e1_d2931e1_d2932e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2930e1_d2931e1_d2932e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"guj1665702720735.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/guj1665702720735.html\" title=\"Allow the use of Japanese Gaiji characters.\">$GAIJI</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2930e1_d2931e1_d2932e1__entry__2\">If the Unicode private area ranged from E000 to\n                        F8FF is needed for your application, set <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$GAIJ</span> to\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2930e1_d2931e1_d2932e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jpa1665702722765.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jpa1665702722765.html\" title=\"Set the data storage format of String fields with the U* packing code to XML or TRX.\">$META_IN_TRX</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2930e1_d2931e1_d2932e1__entry__2\">To let <code class=\"ph codeph\">U*</code>-String fields hold\n                        Unicode characters, set <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$META_IN_TRX</span>=<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2930e1_d2931e1_d2932e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wzv1665702719081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wzv1665702719081.html\" title=\"Specify the character set used for String fields with the W packing code.\">$WIDE_CHAR_BEHAVIOR</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2930e1_d2931e1_d2932e1__entry__2\">If the database only supports Unicode BMP, set\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$WIDE_CHAR_BEHAVIOR</span>=<code class=\"ph codeph\">BMP</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2930e1_d2931e1_d2932e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gzx1665702657590.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gzx1665702657590.html\" title=\"Use the [META_CharSet ] section of the assignment file to map characters in the Uniface meta character set, for example [META_Japanese] or [META_Western], to and from Unicode.\">[META_CharSet]</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2930e1_d2931e1_d2932e1__entry__2\">\n Make your own mappings between Unicode and the meta character set.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2933e1_d2934e1_d2935e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Unicode-Related ProcScript Functions and Statements</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2933e1_d2934e1_d2935e1__entry__1\">\n ProcScript\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2933e1_d2934e1_d2935e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2933e1_d2934e1_d2935e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$string</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2933e1_d2934e1_d2935e1__entry__2\">\n Generate Unicode characters from their codes.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2933e1_d2934e1_d2935e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">fileload</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lfileload</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2933e1_d2934e1_d2935e1__entry__2\">\n Specify the Unicode format in the <var class=\"keyword varname\">CharacterSetName</var> parameter to load a Unicode file into Uniface.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2933e1_d2934e1_d2935e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">filedump</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lfiledump</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qmi1665702875884__table_d2933e1_d2934e1_d2935e1__entry__2\">\n Specify the Unicode format in the <var class=\"keyword varname\">CharacterSetName</var> parameter to write texts into a Unicode file.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531331\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531331\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Unicode-Related Settings and ProcScript Instructions Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Unicode-Related Settings and ProcScript Instructions Assignment settings and ProcScript instructions influence the use of Unicode in your applications. Table 1. Unicode-Related Assignment Settings Setting Description $GAIJI If the Unicode private area ranged from E000 to F8FF is needed for your application, set $GAIJ to 0 . $META_IN_TRX To let U* -String fields hold Unicode characters, set $META_IN_TRX = 0 . $WIDE_CHAR_BEHAVIOR If the database only supports Unicode BMP, set $WIDE_CHAR_BEHAVIOR = BMP . [META_CharSet] Make your own mappings between Unicode and the meta character set. Table 2. Unicode-Related ProcScript Functions and Statements ProcScript Description $string Generate Unicode characters from their codes. fileload , lfileload Specify the Unicode format in the CharacterSetName parameter to load a Unicode file into Uniface. filedump , lfiledump Specify the Unicode format in the CharacterSetName parameter to write texts into a Unicode file. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}